# =============================================================================
# app.py — Ghost Worker / Fraud Detection API
# Deployed on Hugging Face Spaces
#
# Endpoints:
#   GET  /health  — liveness check
#   POST /score   — upload a payroll CSV/Excel and receive a fraud analysis
#   GET  /docs    — Swagger UI (auto-generated by FastAPI)
#
# Detection pipeline:
#   1. Parse uploaded CSV/Excel payroll file
#   2. Detect scan type (Full Scan vs Rinse Scan) based on available columns
#   3. Normalise columns, salary values, and engineer additional features
#   4. Score each employee via an ensemble:
#        Full Scan  → 70% XGBoost (full) + 30% Isolation Forest
#        Rinse Scan → 100% XGBoost (rinse, lightweight)
#   5. Convert raw ensemble probability to a 0–100 trust score
#   6. Assign each employee a payment tier and risk classification
#   7. Generate AI-written audit explanations via Gemini (async, concurrent)
#   8. Return structured JSON conforming to the canonical response schema
#
# Response schema version: 2.0
# =============================================================================

